description.narrative: With UNICEF support, the Ministry of Education formally assessed primary students to evaluate learning outcome levels for the first time in decades which is not only a huge milestone for the sector but also for the country. The assessments were designed for Grade 3 and Grade 6 students, focusing on the learning levels in Spanish and Mathematics.;UNICEF supported the MoE to respond to the Bata explosions through resource mobilization and implementation of emergency interventions.
